ed="T" n="0835b25"/><persName key="A012469">釋惠秀</persName><ptr target="#n2584"/>，俗姓<name>李</name>氏，今<placeName key="PL000000023452"><placeName>東京</placeName><placeName>陳留</placeName></placeName>人也。出離塵<lb
ed="T" n="0835b26"/>垢，慕尚逍遙。初以戒律飾躬，後以禪定<lb
ed="T" n="0835b27"/>為務。於<placeName key="PL000000027770">荊</placeName><placeName key="PL000000027486">郢</placeName>之地，參問祖師<ptr target="#n2585"/>，既了安然，迴<lb
ed="T" n="0835b28"/>依<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛</placeName>邑<placeName key="PL000000023564">天宮寺</placeName>也。<date from-iso="+0684-10-22" key="j19711811978588" to-iso="+0705-02-02">屬</date><persName key="A002099">則天</persName>頻幸<placeName key="PL000000023581">神都</placeName>，而<persName key="A012469">秀</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0835b29"/>道聲聞于<persName key="A002099">后</persName>聽，屢詔入禮重，其於懸記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1165"/>未然<pb ed="T" n="0835c" xml:id="T50.2061.0835c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0835c01"/>事，合同符契。<date notBefore-iso="+0701-11-30" key="j19774281978588" notAfter-iso="+0705-02-02"><name>長安</name>中</date>往<placeName key="PL000000042260">資聖寺</placeName><ptr target="#n2586"/>，唱道化人，<lb
ed="T" n="0835c02"/>翕然<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g768"/>歸向。忽誡禪院弟子，令滅燈燭。有白<lb
ed="T" n="0835c03"/><persName key="A012469">秀</persName>曰：「長明燈可留？」亦令滅之。因說<ptr type="glossary" target="#g442"/>火災難<lb
ed="T" n="0835c04"/>測，不可不備，云甞有寺家，不備火燭佛<lb
ed="T" n="0835c05"/>殿被焚，又有一寺鐘樓遭爇，又有一寺經<lb
ed="T" n="0835c06"/>藏煨燼，殊可痛惜。時眾不喻其旨。至夜遺<lb
ed="T" n="0835c07"/>火，佛殿、鐘樓、經藏三所悉成灰炭。方知<persName key="A012469">秀</persName>預<lb
ed="T" n="0835c08"/>知垂警。又<persName key="A000291">玄宗</persName>在<placeName key="PL000000004130">潞</placeName>邸時<ptr target="#n2587"/>，曾與諸王俱詣<lb
ed="T" n="0835c09"/>問法從容<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1410"/>，留施一笛。<persName key="A000291">玄宗</persName>出去，<persName key="A012469">秀</persName>召弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0835c10"/>曰：「謹掌此笛，後有要時，當獻上也。」及受<lb
ed="T" n="0835c11"/><persName key="A002461">睿宗</persName>傳禪，弟子<persName key="A012470"><anchor xml:id="beg0835004"/>達磨<anchor xml:id="end0835004"/></persName>等方悟其言，取笛以<lb
ed="T" n="0835c12"/>進。<ref type="person" target="#A000291">帝</ref>悅先知，迴賜豐厚。<persName key="A012469">秀</persName>偶示微疾，告誡<lb
ed="T" n="0835c13"/>門人，奄然歸寂。享年一百歲。<persName key="A002473"><persName>燕國公</persName><persName>張說</persName></persName>素<lb
ed="T" n="0835c14"/>所歸心，<anchor xml:id="beg0835sgsz18"/>送<anchor xml:id="end0835sgsz18"/>瘞<placeName key="PL000000023647">龍門山</placeName>。道俗數千人奔會悲悼<lb
ed="T" n="0835c15"/>焉<ptr target="#n2588"/>。</p>
